service.tut.pori.contentanalysis

Class ResultInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.ResultInfo

  • public class ResultInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple class that shows details about a search query. Generally used with lists to indicate the total number of results in case the list itself contains only a partial set of results. ResultInfo should not be present, if not especially requested with data group result_info

    Optional Elements

    • startItem. The requested start item, if available.
    • endItem. The requested end item, if available.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<resultInfo>
  <endItem>2072406070</endItem>
  <resultCount>1128993684691803737</resultCount>
  <startItem>1396760147</startItem>
</resultInfo>
